Class Summary 
Class Description
Connect4
Handles all of the logic related to our Connect4 board game This contains our game board, taking turns, checking win conditions and calling on display from our Connect4TextConsole so that it can display our board to the players
Connect4Client
Our Connect4Client that will connect to our server for playing the game
Connect4ComputerPlayer
Responsible for simulating a computer player in our Connect4 game
Connect4Gui  
Connect4Server
Our Connect4Server that will get connection from the clients, and then create unique game instance threads using these clients together.
Connect4TextConsole
Responsible for running our Connect4 program and displaying the board in the console
